            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1653316833046-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1653316833046-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush the <strong>garlic cloves</strong> by squashing them with the side of a knife (keep the skins on!)</p><p>Add the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, the <strong>crushed garlic</strong>, <strong>remaining dried sage</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 35-40 minutes or until golden and crispy – these are your <strong>herby roasties</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1653316859282-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
