            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's nearly ready, put the<strong> ciabattas</strong> in the oven for 4-5 min or until they're warm and crusty, then carefully slice in half</p><p>Add the <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the reserved pot, cover them with boiling water, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through</p><p>Tip: If the gravy has cooled down, warm it through over a low heat</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
