            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your burgers, spread a little <strong>horseradish mayo</strong> over each <strong>warmed ciabatta base</strong> and <strong>lid</strong>, then sandwich a <strong>beef</strong> <strong>patty</strong>, some <strong>roasted carrots</strong>, and a generous drizzle of <strong>onion gravy </strong>between the base and lid</p><p>Serve the <strong>warmed peas </strong>with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>to the side along with the <strong>remaining roasted carrots</strong>, the <strong>herby roasties </strong>and any<strong> remaining onion gravy</strong> (for dipping!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
